  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 9024d1781799b6f4b9de84bc0207d71a, type: 3}
  m_Name: Spikey_1_Offer
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogData
  Lines:
  - Hey adventurer! My name is Spikey. I'm a woodcutting robot.
  - There are some resources in this world that you can collect.
  - You can use these resources to help you get stronger.
  - See that tree next to us? Try chopping it for some time and then come back to
    me.
